{"tid":1527840,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大 雄 與 胖 虎 打 交。","createTime":"2019-09-01T11:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:32:33.000Z","uid":34399,"like":129,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4717a02da842429f0b386cf807a6179e0f8a85","tid":1527840,"uid":34399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"今早大雄比平常早了回到班房<br />\n看到老師在班房抽煙，老師也看到了他<br />\n老師在上課前向風紀胖虎遞上20元紙幣，要他想想辦法<br />\n大雄進入班房便被胖虎拉住，警告他要小心言行<br />\n<br />\n數日內大雄跟眾多同學和其他老師訴說吸煙事情<br />\n可是大家都覺得無謂搞，多一事不如少一事<br />\n大雄氣憤之下便拿起一枝粉筆丟向胖虎<br />\n胖虎拿出棒球棍打得大雄頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n老師：「大雄丟粉筆，使用暴力破壞班中秩序，而胖虎則盡了風紀的責任。」<br />\n胖虎：「這是我作為風紀的職責，而且想打大雄很久了。我會服從老師的命令，而且又能買零食。」<br />\n<br />\n小夫：「老師和胖虎都是對的，大雄搞事便抵打。」<br />\n靜香：「胖虎好像太暴力了，但大雄丟粉筆也錯。暴力就是不對。」<br />\n出木杉：「不關我事，我要唸書，將來找份好工作。」<br />\n胖妹：「哥哥為了維持秩序，打得手都軟了，都怪大雄你這個暴徒。」<br />\n<br />\n多啦A夢：「你真笨，跟胖虎和老師作對。老師吸煙是很平常的，你不要放大。」<br />\n多啦美：「你才一名小學生，對煙一知半解就學人扮代表。」<br />\n大雄媽媽：「胖虎也有脾氣的，你跟他打就要有心理準備會這樣。」<br />\n大雄爸爸：「這麼一點煙味會怎樣？我小時候可比你吸得多了。」<br />\n<br />\n大雄覺得生活真的很不如意，問多啦A夢借了隨意門。<br />\n他在這裡看到人們要吃樹皮，小朋友會餓死，會被野生動物獵殺<br />\n大雄：「這裡的人好像還要文明一些。」"},{"pid":"57dc6e12f14c42200c505d37656f1d460835dec0","tid":1527840,"uid":273234,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"寧願企喺度食樹皮<br />\n都好好跪喺度賺錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbKHQaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbKHQaA.jpg&h=5496a090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aed94415dc3f63d6ab9b1f2235f301a745f752e","tid":1527840,"uid":300554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 6條命 900被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6fa296577e095e6a48e8e6a456bdf22a9a5006f","tid":1527840,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c29876b9f3127c0a62d29311facfcba7cd34db84","tid":1527840,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"高質留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ad9041353a7f709e5ddda0351fa861c1550dc8","tid":1527840,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"e818afbf6d68ce77888dacb56bb31156f4a36167","tid":1527840,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:21:21.000Z","msg":"搵人理下我 ，支持請留名721 831<br />\n<br />\n《千萬唔好》打爆所有警察出現既地鐵站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51a432913173bfacdeac6b1c46f6bd1cfe08bfe5","tid":1527840,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6e8bdd4f1ba9233adae825e817ee1522e77cd2c","tid":1527840,"uid":200666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:30:07.000Z","msg":"寧死不屈"},{"pid":"ad201d578d8235f9b5f8beea3c79a41b2b832f35","t